{"tid":1668673,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"范國威引用特權法調查警隊濫權","createTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T06:45:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ac996a2552a3b20bd67d1fd64611baaed6e51fe3","tid":1668673,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:21:44.000Z","msg":"新民主同盟立法會議員范國威提出, 在立法會引用特力及特權條例, 調查在反修例示威中, 警員濫權的問題.<br />\n<br />\n        范國威提出的議案內容, 包括, 調查在示威中, 有警員執行職務時無展示警員編號、 無出示委任證、 用面罩遮掩面部的情況, 及調查有警員涉嫌濫用武力和武器, 以及特區政府在警方行動中的角色責任等.<br />\n<br />\n        立法會主席梁君彥批准議案, 可以在下星期3的大會中提出.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20191022140811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20191022140811&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f38e33ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20191022140811</a>"},{"pid":"32553f3b42652b3fc5fe0447eb8161cecb70c1d6","tid":1668673,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"歸邊議案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a660631beeb49b74806ef22e95674ad77c3033a","tid":1668673,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:29:09.000Z","msg":"建制一樣全數反對，無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5690f54fcdda432f3f16c6a1692b3e40b72b323e","tid":1668673,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:30:01.000Z","msg":"不如提埋彈劾柒婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a856c737b261a0dc1688a6c0ec3379275456d3","tid":1668673,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a660631beeb49b74806ef22e95674ad77c3033a","tid":1668673,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:29:09.000Z","msg":"建制一樣全數反對，無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:30:43.000Z","msg":"因為佢地根本無壓力，反對左又無害"},{"pid":"3c7c54dfd01999a4d3ede810fef92f134c217af0","tid":1668673,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:32:36.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n為左健康著想 以後邊個地區放tg 個個地區就罷買一星期<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668290\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668290</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5d6901587b1448c7e1f93de49519f9a849d923f7","tid":1668673,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"}]}